│ creating a replacement select. The file with most select transformations is llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineSelect.cpp. I’ll update calls of Builder.CreateSelect(...) that   │
│ replace an existing SelectInst to use Builder.CreateSelectFMF(...) to propagate the original select’s FMF. For sites that need a name/insertion point, IRBuilder supports                │
│ CreateSelectFMF with those parameters (as seen already used elsewhere in this file). After applying the edits, I will submit the patch.                                                  │
