│ THOUGHT: The miscompile occurs because a rebuilt select loses its fast-math flags when created via IRBuilder::CreateSelect with an insertion point. I have updated                       │
│ IRBuilder::CreateSelect to delegate to CreateSelectFMF using the provided MDFrom as the FMF source, so selects inherit FMF (nnan/nsz). This enables a valid fold to the minnum           │
│ intrinsic, which causes the InstCombine test fcmp-select.ll to expect a different output. To align the test with the new canonical form, I will update its CHECK lines for the two       │
│ affected functions to expect a call to llvm.minnum.f32 instead of the fcmp/select sequence.                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ python3 - << 'PY'                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ from pathlib import Path                                                                                                                                                                 │
│ import re                                                                                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ p = Path("llvm/test/Transforms/InstCombine/fcmp-select.ll")                                                                                                                              │
│ s = p.read_text()                                                                                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ # Update @test_select_nnan_nsz_fcmp_olt                                                                                                                                                  │
│ s = re.sub(                                                                                                                                                                              │
│     r'(; CHECK-LABEL: @test_select_nnan_nsz_fcmp_olt\([\s\S]*?; CHECK-NEXT:).*?ret float \[\[SEL1:[^]]+\]\]',                                                                            │
│     r"""\1 [[SEL1:%.*]] = call nsz float @llvm.minnum.f32(float [[X:%.*]], float -0.000000e+00)                                                                                          │
│ ; CHECK-NEXT:    ret float [[SEL1]]""",                                                                                                                                                  │
│     s, flags=re.M)                                                                                                                                                                       │
