│ NoNaNs/NoInfs, and preserve NoSignedZeros only if MDFrom is a SelectInst to avoid enabling unrelated canonicalizations.                                                                  │
│ - I’ll update llvm/lib/IR/IRBuilder.cpp accordingly, using dyn_cast_or_null for safety, and then run the validation.                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
